text: Norberto Murara Neto (born 19 July 1989), commonly known as Neto, is a Brazilian professional footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for Premier League club AFC Bournemouth. For the 2024-2025 Premier League season he is loaned out to Arsenal F.C. ==References== Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Footballers from Minas Gerais Category:Brazilian association football goalkeepers Category:FC Barcelona players Category:Premier League players Category:AFC Bournemouth players Category:Footballers at the 2012 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic medalists in football Category:Medalists at the 2012 Summer Olympics
